					<ul>
						<li>Anonymous - We don't collect any kind of data</li>
						<li>Free and always free - We won't charge you anything</li>
						<li>Fast - ShortKin.gq runs on the best cloud providers</li>
						<li>No ads - Unlike other shorteners, ShortKin.gq doesn't have ads. Users won't notice anything.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col mdl-cell--12-col-phone">
					<!-- King -->
					<img src="/King.jpg" alt="ShortKin.gq">
				</div>
			</div>
		  </main>
		</div>
		<script src="shortkingq.js"></script>
	</body>
